[The formation of this task force and the identification of specific goals is some good news that comes out of this otherwise worrisome spread of chikungunya virus in the Caribbean. However, at the present time there are no measures available that can halt the further spread of the virus in the Americas, as Scott Weaver pointed out. - Mod.TY]
